{"tid":557862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[非搵食]學/考英文，你問我答","createTime":"2018-02-11T17:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T02:50:58.000Z","uid":91565,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e780b645360ae9d47de4dd77ed96b845ed5e036","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講明先，非搵食，<span style=\"color: red;\">搵食死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你有以下既英文問題，歡迎問下我<br />\n<br />\n1. DSE 英文考試相關<br />\n2. IELTS <br />\n3. Grammar<br />\n<br />\n英文系BA/MA畢業，畢業教書到而家<br />\n<br />\n對於學英文我想講既係<br />\n<br />\n1. grammar 係一個語言背後既框架，想用一種語言用得好，grammar底一定要firm <br />\n<br />\n2. grammar 大部分都無需死背，因為其實邏輯性非常強，一理通馬國明<br />\n<br />\n3. 無必要學一啲過份艱深既生字同過份花巧既句構，因為說到底語言既功能就係溝通，最緊要係你要有同邊個講野既意識<br />\n<br />\n4. 從錯誤中學習，面對自己既錯既時候最緊要係知點解錯同點樣改，唔係無進步"},{"pid":"966ef40d1dcaccdf5a79e865611431f018f16bf7","tid":557862,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"380d61fa3bcfa4d13b6adbe96c331b809b8c9de5","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966ef40d1dcaccdf5a79e865611431f018f16bf7","tid":557862,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:26:11.000Z","msg":"咩時候英文U?"},{"pid":"097049910bf1b6df7e66ecbfd60299d5904e5aec","tid":557862,"uid":142009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"ielts 筆試邊到有卷可以操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5f524760f144fa6014ecaa63461ee193fa84c2","tid":557862,"uid":4938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"可以點樣提升IELTS<br />\n本身得5.5<br />\n想去到6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d56f7951c4ce15e1a21e4a2c6f74b5df43cb69","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc