br />\n大學去左英國讀法律 之後讀埋執業課程<br />\n好彩搵到間大行請我<br />\n做過三個Department 成日啲野都俾人改到七彩<br />\n<br />\n我已經成日跟Template 唔跟啲部份 都係全紅<br />\n不過未俾人炒 當無事繼續做啦惟有 不過無進步"},{"pid":"36dca0ef446e40c09fbcdc6e5e2058f4a598eeb2","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"237d05996609ec2b4fe0ca3727e55aace85ef91e","tid":557862,"uid":4938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e13bd00a9e7e8615e0df0ed914ded9d6b87c984e","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c5f524760f144fa6014ecaa63461ee193fa84c2","tid":557862,"uid":4938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"可以點樣提升IELTS<br />\n本身得5.5<br />\n想去到6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"你最弱邊方面，講多少少我再答你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"應該得listening 有6分 其他5.5<br />\n自己覺得writing 最弱 其次係reading<br />\n係咪真係要背返多啲詞彙同操返好grammar <br />\n因為我grammar 極廢（已經買左本English grammar in use同IELTS 11,12）"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"reading 有技巧做，多做試題有幫助<br />\n靠技巧可以提升半個grade<br />\n嘗試係題目入面搵關鍵詞<br />\n你會發現個關鍵詞係篇文入面會出現返<br />\n跟住就豁然開朗<br />\n答案就在附近<br />\n<br />\nwriting academic 的話多睇範文<br />\n特別task 1 其實有共同既框架<br />\n跟住框架一步步做<br />\ntask 2 除左內容之外時間控制都好重要<br />\n因為要四十分鐘寫250字<br />\n試下用十三句寫曬成篇文<br />\n<br />\ngrammar 重要，但做練習或自學時最緊要既係清concept<br />\ngrammar in use 一個unit未做到全中的話唔好落下一個<br />\n<br />\nvocab 我覺得係夠就得，重點係無必要學啲好難既字"},{"pid":"f40d37146451ed9f4a8da51982ef936cc142e999","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b227075eb9b1c683501ffadfd7cc76662509fcf2","tid":557862,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e72ad0d9bb2133c1fcc6ddf0d91e6ba2956980","tid":557862,"uid":91565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68aff130b890e891b16094813ccc38aec8c0d0ca","tid":557862,"uid":127052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:37:06.000Z",